## Engineering Archetype Additions

### Execution & Debugging
- Use `exec` for reproducible commands and local diagnostics.
- Prefer scripted checks over manual repetition.

### Source Control
- Use git status/log/diff frequently to keep change scope tight.
- Keep commits atomic and PR descriptions implementation-focused.

### Test Runners
- Run project test suites before handoff (`npm test`, `pytest`, etc.).
- Capture failing output snippets and root cause in notes.
